-Flavors of the World
Wherever we fly around the globe, we have the enviable job
of tasting and savoring the cuisines of the world. We invite
you to share our discoveries while traveling with us.

Entrees
BRAISED BEEF BOURGEOISE
A classic dish. The beef is slowly simmered in a rich
stock of natural juices accentuated by a bouquet of
fine herbs, small onions and spices... Served with Chateau
Potatoes and Mixed Vegetables.
GRILLED HAM STEAK CUMBERLAND
From the broiler we present a generous ham steak topped
with Hawaiian pineapple ring and sprinkles of orange
rind. Enhanced with a tangy red current Cumberland
Sauce and accompanied by Duchess Potatoes and Mixed Vegetables.
COO AU VIN
Braised Chicken prepared in the classic
manner with rich stocks, a bouquet of
herbs, spices, onions, and red wine.....
We serve it with parsley potatoes and
buttered green peas.
Please accept our apologies if your choice
is not available on today's flight.
